    <p>I love playing “futbol” (soccer in the USA, football for the rest of the English world) with friends, but I must confess that it has been a couple of years since I last ran the whole hour ^^. It doesn’t help that we are going through a pandemic.</p>

    <p>I also like listening to music from various styles. If I had to choose a couple of records I would pick:</p>
