  </li>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Other things you might want to share.</strong></p>

    <p>I would like to thank Reshama Shaikh and the whole Data Umbrella crew for the amazing work they have done. The sprints and all the other activities are tremendously helpful to the underrepresented people in data science and the open-source world.</p>
